---
title: "Frequently asked questions"
description: "Do you have questions about Folkingebrew or our beers? Here you'll find a selection of the most frequently asked questions."
sitemap_priority: 0.8
---
<%
questions = data["faq"]
%>

<header class="normal-page-header">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <h1>
      <%= t("pages.faq.title") %>
    </h1>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="faq medium-row">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="row">
      <p>
        Below you will find answers to the questions we get asked a lot. If your question isn't answered, just drop us an email through <%= link_to "our contact form", "/contact.html" %> or get in touch on our social feeds (<%= link_to "Facebook", "https://www.facebook.com/Folkingebrew-167577637289407/", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %> or <%= link_to "Instagram", "https://www.instagram.com/folkingebrew/", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %>).
      </p>
      <% questions.each do |question| %>
        <h2>
          <%= question.q %>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <%= question.a.to_s %>
        </p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
